  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Iron & Steel transformation event: hot rolling of EAF billets into a batch",
    "of S500B reinforcing bar. Input = billets (by quantity), output = the rebar",
    "batch (by EPC). The heat number that ties the output to its cast travels in",
    "ilmd as an event-level extension property (prefixed eusteel:). Static product",
    "attributes (steel identification, MTC, recycled content) live INSIDE",
    "masterDataAvailableFor on the output product entry, where gs1: is the ambient",
    "vocab so GS1 terms are bare and extension terms keep their context alias.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,",
    "                              eusteel=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/iron-steel/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
